		sail along the rugged California coast, accompanied by native dolphin
		riding along the bow wave of your majestic sailing vessel. Teach
		your kids the value of self-sufficiency at sea, learning the basics
		of navigation and safe seamanship. Open their eyes to a world beyond
		the television set, and experience firsthand the wonders of the sea.
		Your own personal USCG-certified Captain will instruct you on seafaring
		basics; or, you may relax and just take in the many sights that the
		Channel Islands have to offer.
